# Keep essential data like datasets if needed, but ignore large generated outputs
# artifacts might be okay to keep if they are small plots, but typically derived artifacts are ignored.
artifacts/

# Local verification and stress test scripts (optional)
# User wants to add gitignore for repo, usually we keep dev scripts but ignore their outputs.
# I'll keep the scripts but ignore potential logs they produce if any.
*.log

